{"tid":100131,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"舊年夏天　毒遊台中、南投、合歡山","createTime":"2017-01-29T17:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T14:01:34.000Z","uid":33727,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a2b18ba32b09e81adc66e2834437403525a1fe09","tid":100131,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T17:39:26.000Z","msg":"見過年悶悶地, 不如打下遊記 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本來想打12月去京阪神, 但旅遊台好似已經好多日本遊記<br />\n咁就不如打下台灣先　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實已經係舊年五月頭既事<br />\n呢次目標主要係上合歡山<br />\n不過其實上去之前都唔知係上去做乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係覺得高山好靚又有交通到, 要去睇下<br />\n<br />\n好, 廢話講完即刻開始出發 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 1<br />\n<br />\n又係坐快運, 而家呢班夜機已經無左<br />\n其實以前早去晚回時間真係好好 <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/9LiCpL0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9LiCpL0.jpg&h=00e0dc0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCheck In 時地勤問我坐緊急通道位好唔好, 梗係即刻話好啦<br />\n上機後有個空姐來Check登機證, 之後解釋注意事項<br />\n問題係呢個空姐應該係日/韓籍, D英文好難聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後咩都聽唔明, 就咁OKOK就算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zhqEhWF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzhqEhWF.jpg&h=dc8dfba0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落機後搭巴士去市區, 又多人又慢<br />\n就快搭到訓著 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/l3JDouj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fl3JDouj.jpg&h=e8898f27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到酒店丟低D行李即刻出一中街搵野食<br />\n已經九點幾<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/RCybL2S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRCybL2S.jpg&h=bbb5ddbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實事隔太耐, 已經唔係好記得食過乜<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/KsB9SKh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKsB9SKh.jpg&h=180edb15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舟車勞頓其實無乜胃口, 食左少少野就番酒店<br />\n頂樓有個common room, 望出去都幾開揚<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/PmfBjAP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPmfBjAP.jpg&h=eeb1286a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚住呢D類似Hostel形式的床位<br />\n因為星期六, 要650台幣一晚<br />\n張相係第二朝影<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/MdhWfna.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMdhWfna.jpg&h=80ef2b3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 1咁就完左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽日繼續打, 希望唔好爛尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42fd58dbac931754f23b8c26b9569465c2d34eb8","tid":100131,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T18:06:36.000Z","msg":"好似打得太少, 打多少少先訓<br />\n<br />\nDay 2<br />\n<br />\n今日開始上山喇<br />\n<br />\n好難得去旅行都一早八點幾起身<br />\n九點三去到車站準備搭9:25班車上清境轉車<br />\n最後當然係已經滿座 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有目送大家上車<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5xI8bSE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5xI8bSE.jpg&h=9c758755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後ON居居等左半個鐘先有下一班車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n途中風景<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/UvTMaqX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUvTMaqX.jpg&h=570223b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n地理中心碑 - 台灣正中心<br />\n其實路口呢個牌唔係正中心, 真正正中心係後面個公園入面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/EUWhZVz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEUWhZVz.jpg&h=72813a0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上清境條路彎彎曲曲, 好難影相<br />\n全部相唔係濛就係應該樹呀燈柱呀之類 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢張算係最清楚<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/FTrpOsx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFTrpOsx.jpg&h=0c15c50a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搭左兩個半鐘車終於到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jJw8F61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjJw8F61.jpg&h=0f8fbd6b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n台灣人好似好鐘意周圍整個LOVE字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/TLykNwT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTLykNwT.jpg&h=857fe2d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再上合歡山就無野好食, 喇喇臨食個飯先<br />\n呢度1xx台幣, 其實遊客區黎講都唔係貴啦<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/6uhjCKK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F6uhjCKK.jpg&h=a673ab37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見仲有時間就周圍行下<br />\n其實之前已經黎過, 都無咩大改變<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/BOXeLAR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBOXeLAR.jpg&h=e89625b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小瑞士花園<br />\n個感覺好搵笨, 無入過去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/3oX6maK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3oX6maK.jpg&h=8c4e471f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/wAWspUs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwAWspUs.jpg&h=bfed8122&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n差不多時間就返去搭車喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/uAEfiN8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuAEfiN8.jpg&h=e0d8f650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n待續 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e4e41f82112e9e247c7073e1c382caad7b692c","tid":100131,"uid":74163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-29T18:17:15.000Z","msg":"獨遊台灣有冇識到囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e97e68365585af71989a790859f4bd37318749","tid":100131,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T04:35:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>獨遊台灣有冇識到囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n獨遊可能會識到<br />\n但毒遊係唔會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n淨係識到男人"},{"pid":"4cf3d41be146e41fa9130f67fa62c88374d921ce","tid":100131,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T05:31:26.000Z","msg":"打打下竟然hang機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n繼續<br />\n<br />\n一路搭車上山, 見到D雲<br />\n先開始有自己係高山上面既感覺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/1LP8vwO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1LP8vwO.jpg&h=b330b66f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/pcWmTtx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpcWmTtx.jpg&h=7bd4138d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為有溫差, 一落車即刻要著番件外套 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗番朝早搭車之前仲熱到一身汗<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Aqh36px.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FAqh36px.jpg&h=5ddd7fc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚住呢度, 好似要900一晚<br />\n其實都唔平, 不過3千幾米高山有得住算好啦<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/9EPscQ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9EPscQ1.jpg&h=7b230e3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知連舖直張墊褥都唔夠位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/A5ygs6c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FA5ygs6c.jpg&h=8bf910d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一行出門口就見到雲海<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/oRN2tbr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FoRN2tbr.jpg&h=eaad75d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度係兩個縣既交界點<br />\n過左呢個牌就係花蓮縣<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/j6JR4Az.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fj6JR4Az.jpg&h=05b5a440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n夏天既溫度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/q4gXMng.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fq4gXMng.jpg&h=98f853c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已經4點幾, 仲有少少時間可以行下石門山<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/OLgsXPk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOLgsXPk.jpg&h=cd24a12f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天氣麻麻地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 灰濛濛咁<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/R2mKlsk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FR2mKlsk.jpg&h=fe844330&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好快已經行左大半<br />\n但其實開始已經索氣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 少做運動<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/eo5dle7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Feo5dle7.jpg&h=8c7970da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到達, 打個卡先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n慢行都係半個鐘就上到頂<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/a9EgMo6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fa9EgMo6.jpg&h=78091276&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五月上山其實幾好, 遇到開花季節<br />\n成個山頭都係花 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/uKMmZSD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuKMmZSD.jpg&h=da1e790e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s5gbr0E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs5gbr0E.jpg&h=f6fe7b08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽日計畫<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/stktYQw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FstktYQw.jpg&h=eee149ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於見到太陽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但其實就快天黑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hu8Z3kC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fhu8Z3kC.jpg&h=f9af38b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雀仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/n4xZlvO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fn4xZlvO.jpg&h=132ae170&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係天黑, 係時候番歸<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/xUlFkuS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxUlFkuS.jpg&h=05881626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說其實住宿係包埋晚餐同早餐既<br />\n不過食落就...嗯 唔好要求太高咁囉<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qQrvoF3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqQrvoF3.jpg&h=68980ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後送上死點圖一張 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0yBIlMo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0yBIlMo.jpg&h=9903ce4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n傻瓜機影星, 係咁上下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDay 2完"},{"pid":"b0ed9cc31c211d53e02597cf6627ff02d4af9c5d","tid":100131,"uid":74163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:16:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>獨遊台灣有冇識到囡囡<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n獨遊可能會識到<br />\n但毒遊係唔會 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n淨係識到男人</blockquote><br />\n住青旅好似易識人多d 識下台仔都好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8ac94d256d44f9b60490facb378083342797cb","tid":100131,"uid":22913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T07:23:31.000Z","msg":"留名先 3月打算去台灣行山影相"},{"pid":"2997795476f4a0e30a4909f1f5bbf493d9b713b5","tid":100131,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-30T17:25:00.000Z","msg":"繼續<br />\n<br />\nDay 3<br />\n<br />\n一早四點幾起身試下有無日出睇<br />\n行番出大馬路, 嘩多人到呢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/kchsqs4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fkchsqs4.jpg&h=7b44204b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但個天係咁樣<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/3Hd98C2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3Hd98C2.jpg&h=80bde863&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後梗係咩都睇唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/NPMSf2s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNPMSf2s.jpg&h=a1fdd201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n都係番歸恰多陣好過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/d2COlqv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fd2COlqv.jpg&h=25013b2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然最後係訓唔著 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n轆到八點幾起身去食早餐<br />\n我既評語依然係...嗯<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/96JNtlS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F96JNtlS.jpg&h=f10e0723&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天氣其實又差唔晒<br />\n雖然有雲但都幾好陽光<br />\n(所以之後就出事)<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/t1tkmlT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ft1tkmlT.jpg&h=a193e365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來準備由松雪樓行去武嶺<br />\n點知遇到尋晚同房一位auntie渣車走<br />\n咁有順風車就梗係搭啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/cxNW16p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FcxNW16p.jpg&h=7df228b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n輕輕鬆鬆就去到武嶺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後面係剛剛踩單車上來既哥哥仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/VnymwSJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVnymwSJ.jpg&h=7d4c4bc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又遇到雀仔<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/BiStivy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBiStivy.jpg&h=a2df1513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHea左一陣就出發去今日第一個目標<br />\n就係對面山頭個條路<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/1baNkPg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1baNkPg.jpg&h=7de08f20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實都唔少人踩單車上黎<br />\n我已經見到3-4個<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/18pdu7w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F18pdu7w.jpg&h=c065c4aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n得一條車路仲要彎彎曲曲<br />\n真係要小心睇路<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/puvqmN7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpuvqmN7.jpg&h=970a98ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Jyo70xU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJyo70xU.jpg&h=5812a89d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實係石屎路一條<br />\n好闊 (可以比車上落, 當然唔係人人上得)<br />\n好易行<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Z8eleEY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FZ8eleEY.jpg&h=38ff1118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n望番落去下面D車好得意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zf2eAV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fzf2eAV7.jpg&h=23c3b090&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又係雀<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/9LgXf3R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9LgXf3R.jpg&h=f36216f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越行越高<br />\n雖然睇住google map行, 知道未到頂<br />\n不過應該都就到啦<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/RD59p7P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRD59p7P.jpg&h=1ee75bef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢舊係乜? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打仗用?<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qTFzGj3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqTFzGj3.jpg&h=50cd14e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係因為山頂有好多呢D電子(?)設備<br />\n所以有車路上黎<br />\n成條路都好易行<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/l591mF9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fl591mF9.jpg&h=5c2d2540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n到達 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又係打卡相<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/emfC9Xn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FemfC9Xn.jpg&h=c24d555d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐低一陣, 又做左攝影師幫人渣機影相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"547b30f1f2860b6385f7120a6de4343f862646ec","tid":100131,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T06:40:15.000Z","msg":"山頂風景 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/aLrkypD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FaLrkypD.jpg&h=496da9a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n準備落山先發現點解咁多人行小路上黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/97hjHYC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F97hjHYC.jpg&h=8405b194&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁就不如行返小路落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qaRh4hr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqaRh4hr.jpg&h=65a0353f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對面山頭 - 呢D係用黎種野?<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/iKI3J0y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FiKI3J0y.jpg&h=e31f6337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行行下開始諗會唔會唔小心跌落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/9dxSBSj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9dxSBSj.jpg&h=0b4f1164&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後都係行番大路<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/WEDh91P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWEDh91P.jpg&h=50b87698&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n番到武嶺, 今次唔係單車<br />\n而係電單車團 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/UXpGHW5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUXpGHW5.jpg&h=ee4fbaac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不要看我, 看路 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/uthawLq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuthawLq.jpg&h=746827e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行番落去松雪樓<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/MHt7K21.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMHt7K21.jpg&h=8b0e26b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天氣開始變差 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/4Y8qOxR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4Y8qOxR.jpg&h=b101b28e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n午餐 - 求其食<br />\n實際上都無咩可以選擇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/TLBc8Jt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTLBc8Jt.jpg&h=87582195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坐係戶外食, 食食下開始落雨<br />\n好彩無幾耐就停左<br />\n之後就出現<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/YUvRNu7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYUvRNu7.jpg&h=50365b89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n既然出太陽, 咁就向下一個目標出發吧<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/i0HsNNC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fi0HsNNC.jpg&h=d6480218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"b97541d6ce3dd279f0d72099403aeaeb2e6e754d","tid":100131,"uid":75452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:02:40.000Z","msg":"巴打無去埋阿里山？"},{"pid":"dd6a47de15ec0abc917cb40303aa76a4badee790","tid":100131,"uid":33777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcf1b545c538d7835623501289b4f6ff31b8ad7","tid":100131,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T12:22:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打無去埋阿里山？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無，今次淨係去五日四夜<br />\n第一日仲要夜機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都無時間去多幾度"},{"pid":"9ebf5f78901a2e967872413797c11ac5445275a0","tid":100131,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T16:41:43.000Z","msg":"繼續Day 3<br />\n<br />\n向合歡東峰出發之前, 先比山上既花引左去<br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/D6Dgzwo.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FD6Dgzwo.jpg&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfBy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=c3d6dcd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/D6Dgzwo.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n影完一輪先發現嗰個方向係上唔到山 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n惟有行番轉頭<br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/VFkGg56.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVFkGg56.jpg&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfBy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=11e735ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/VFkGg56.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n開始慢慢行上山 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上合歡東峰條路基本上大部分都係梯級<br />\n開頭慢慢行都OK, 行行下就開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多年前有吊車, 比人冬天上山滑雪, 但已經荒廢<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/rcMwAEv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrcMwAEv.jpg&h=dd8bc2fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一路上就遇到好多人落山.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係咪太晏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (當時係4點左右)<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/EK0v1SN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FEK0v1SN.jpg&h=fe3d1d60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行多人拎轉頭望<br />\n就見到開始起大霧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/d43zQCK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fd43zQCK.jpg&h=7b91252d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n吊車遺跡<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/eGALHSq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FeGALHSq.jpg&h=8a78edc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越上越少人, 開始有D淆底<br />\n始終自己一個人上山係有D危險<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/nZdSg6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FnZdSg6e.jpg&h=dba42f08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n問落山D人山上仲有無人<br />\n好彩佢地答有, 咁先安心D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/UKbCocG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FUKbCocG.jpg&h=87516fc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行左超過一個鐘樓梯<br />\n終於就快到<br />\n山上又真係有兩個人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來係今朝係合歡主峰我幫佢地影相, 傾左幾句既男人<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/lxmwCY8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FlxmwCY8.jpg&h=494bd817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上山頂諗住影張打卡相<br />\n一上到去......... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/B0Wn3io.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FB0Wn3io.jpg&h=04042c37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大霧到乜都睇唔到<br />\n你話張相係PS都得架啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過左一陣, 都係散得少少<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/qBdO7Ai.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqBdO7Ai.jpg&h=db13b932&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落番去同兩位男人吹左陣水<br />\n佢地都落山了, 咁我就梗係跟埋一齊<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/oe5gddy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Foe5gddy.jpg&h=c5482e0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講左咁耐, 其實我唔係好識分雲同霧 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hu9htnh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fhu9htnh.jpg&h=80e1a190&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日最後一張相<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/wU42TwW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwU42TwW.jpg&h=14d4509a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落山後實在係太攰, 同兩位男士講bye bye後<br />\n就即刻番住宿抖左一陣, 差D連飯都唔想食<br />\n成晚一張相都無影過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 3 完<br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"439a2a6350fba1ba61b5f7f43ec205e75ffb6c26","tid":100131,"uid":29754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T07:34:53.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"1c9cbffac13f823b3fe3aa97d8d620fce41c856f","tid":100131,"uid":63177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:22:00.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"791506eb12fa486b3b4899f15236b7473df865fe","tid":100131,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:28:43.000Z","msg":"今日呢篇會短D <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay 4<br />\n<br />\n一早起身, 其實都訓得唔好架喇<br />\n不過都要執好野準備撤退<br />\n咁就介紹下呢兩晚住宿地點 滑雪山莊<br />\n六人房, 真係除左六張床舖之外都無位剩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/pkgH7Sa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpkgH7Sa.jpg&h=7d81af68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好似好日式既趟門<br />\n基本上係隔唔到音, 走廊有人講野係聽得到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/QASAM99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQASAM99.jpg&h=664cdef3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n包早晚餐, 都係係松雪樓餐廳度食<br />\n松雪樓係高級D類似酒店既住宿, 但超難BOOK<br />\n每次食飯都要行呢條大斜路上去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夜晚仲要無燈, 要用電話照路<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fVOJXoD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfVOJXoD.jpg&h=bc8a412d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由松雪樓望向滑雪山莊<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/phNQsch.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FphNQsch.jpg&h=3647a4a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n松雪樓大門, 當時裝修緊<br />\n距離馬路係1分鐘步程<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/wkpnUQC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwkpnUQC.jpg&h=4e52ddaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拎住行李去等巴士<br />\n見到一早已經好多人上左山<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/WD3JF7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWD3JF7d.jpg&h=76d30b68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同合歡山講Bye Bye <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/YQSNzvj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYQSNzvj.jpg&h=2247336b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到霧社落車轉車<br />\n旁邊有呢個霧社事件紀念公園<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/uufwDCo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuufwDCo.jpg&h=33c0f602&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實我就無睇賽德克巴萊<br />\n所以都唔係好清楚發生過咩事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Rv5q0sm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRv5q0sm.jpg&h=1645e826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n淨係知同抗日有關 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/lhCQfWP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FlhCQfWP.jpg&h=00dd9bb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉左個圈就返去巴士站, 旁邊有人係度賣生果<br />\n間好多日無食生果, 買左兩隻蕉食<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/8uSkH57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8uSkH57.jpg&h=f2a3d412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個感覺係... 唔似平時超級市場買個D咁精緻<br />\n有D Raw, 野生既感覺 <br />\n<br />\n搭左20分鐘巴士黎到一個被遺棄的遊客區<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/LzF4c27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLzF4c27.jpg&h=8a311b99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"1802939cb8e6a7d7f1cbf420ea07792bdb1f42de","tid":100131,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:37:07.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"b63dbee7fe8466c0f0212dd8a5d3f5700badc46b","tid":100131,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T07:41:32.000Z","msg":"用留名功能劉鳴先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903f8c78c65786484e79e424422f52b7cc24c9c3","tid":100131,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:14:51.000Z","msg":"偷懶左幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 繼續<br />\n<br />\n節錄Wikipedia 「廬山溫泉」<br />\n<br />\n2008年9月12日，辛樂克颱風重創廬山溫泉，多家飯店嚴重毀損。<br />\n<br />\n2011年3月，經經濟部中央地質調查所調查發現，認為廬山北坡母安山只要雨量超過800毫米，就可能嚴重位移，爆發嚴重災情。<br />\n南投縣政府擔憂廬山溫泉區成為小林村第二，到了2011年6月初，決定斥資20多億賠償金集體遷村，要全部搬到36公里外的埔里鎮福興里。<br />\n<br />\n2012年5月31日，南投縣政府公告廢止廬山溫泉區，但廬山溫泉業者表示不滿，先公告廢止溫泉區卻不先安置業者。<br />\n<br />\n2016年7月，南投縣政府投入30餘億元開發福興農場為溫泉區，預定在8月發包，最晚得花兩年時間才能安置廬山溫泉僅存48家業者，屆時以往的廬山溫泉將從地圖消失。<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n而家既廬山, 基本上係等死的狀態<br />\n平日下午大街得幾個人<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/OWKrqHk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOWKrqHk.jpg&h=e60f399c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係呢條河當年洪水氾濫<br />\n開始左廬山溫泉既沒落<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5yMfm9P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5yMfm9P.jpg&h=6430fc75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n得番個空殼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Drlp8iI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDrlp8iI.jpg&h=7fd5ae80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廬山溫泉 - 天下第一泉石碑<br />\n今日只剩一池死水<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/wIUZ9lW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwIUZ9lW.jpg&h=69054bcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n似乎係未開業就結業 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/2N0EgC1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2N0EgC1.jpg&h=b082ada9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行入D<br />\n基本上呢度已經係無行人<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/9m88vNE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9m88vNE.jpg&h=d38d4a9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各大溫泉酒店抽溫泉水既水管<br />\n好似係<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/FaGTnMC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFaGTnMC.jpg&h=32471af2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n裡面有舖頭?<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/dDSa67J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdDSa67J.jpg&h=363efb60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔敢入去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n翻轉頭<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/gEm8Aoe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgEm8Aoe.jpg&h=946b0cf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫停營業 (無了期地)<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/mEZP20U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmEZP20U.jpg&h=f9a29ddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美食廣場..... 既殘骸<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HPVzeie.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHPVzeie.jpg&h=78803d13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n蔣公行館<br />\n仲有人打理嗎?<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/QkTYJyp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQkTYJyp.jpg&h=855cfe99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人去樓空<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Sx0qir6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSx0qir6.jpg&h=b33924a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢度本來係一間全家<br />\n最後都執左<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/DsxKvxs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDsxKvxs.jpg&h=89d3434a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然唔係成個廬山都係死城<br />\n河兩岸都有D舖頭有開門<br />\n呢D距離河岸比較遠既酒店依然做緊生意<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Yj7xpI6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYj7xpI6.jpg&h=cd5fce8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再見廬山 (應該都唔會再見)<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Va4M5jr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVa4M5jr.jpg&h=3c994ee2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n番埔里途中經過 - 觀音橋<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/4ozo6Ou.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4ozo6Ou.jpg&h=85fa2ed8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係埔里市區求其食D野<br />\n呢度好似100蚊台幣左右, 好抵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Ybi4ttS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FYbi4ttS.jpg&h=d0da36fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n就番台中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/rKh73ZM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrKh73ZM.jpg&h=3b4e784c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n待續"},{"pid":"6929334ecc96a1924de31166da39c64fe23fc484","tid":100131,"uid":14291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:29:05.000Z","msg":"唔錯啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫你推推"},{"pid":"bbb6375c641652489ef046ff36fe6f92f0fa864d","tid":100131,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T17:43:16.000Z","msg":"打打下真係爛尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n餘下既行程基本上係台中HEA遊<br />\n由於之前已經去過兩次<br />\n基本上都無咩行程可言<br />\n<br />\n宮原眼科<br />\n好似次次都會入去行下<br />\n但從來都無買過野 (亦無興趣買) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/pyI9GLJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FpyI9GLJ.jpg&h=465a4f14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊台中火車站<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/ErVUOaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FErVUOaf.jpg&h=6414fe05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n車站內 - 一貫台鐵風格<br />\n老老土土的顏色<br />\n上面傳統加過時停用既時間表 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/TGtuAZo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FTGtuAZo.jpg&h=5a8bc204&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一中街<br />\n今次唔係搵野食<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HCID4BE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHCID4BE.jpg&h=dad976ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比較北面既一部分 以賣衫為主<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/kIgtalj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkIgtalj.jpg&h=bdb16ad6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉去逢甲<br />\n結果落大雨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成個夜市當堂好少人<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/uSLSD7X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FuSLSD7X.jpg&h=c65f655b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n越落越大... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zQIMP7h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzQIMP7h.jpg&h=3f3c8ed4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去完日本之後就覺得<br />\n好熟口面.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/B61lm54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FB61lm54.jpg&h=001568ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後以蚵仔煎結束呢一日<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/j5T4JFD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fj5T4JFD.jpg&h=f99133ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"febda1f2a5b9aa4550cb575bbdb573baf6cffc5d","tid":100131,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T08:31:40.000Z","msg":"宮原眼科食雪糕架喎"},{"pid":"20e5351f542026a6224f8d13213cfb8f6e8becb9","tid":100131,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T09:10:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見過年悶悶地, 不如打下遊記 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本來想打12月去京阪神, 但旅遊台好似已經好多日本遊記<br />\n咁就不如打下台灣先　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實已經係舊年五月頭既事<br />\n呢次目標主要係上合歡山<br />\n不過其實上去之前都唔知係上去做乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只係覺得高山好靚又有交通到, 要去睇下<br />\n<br />\n好, 廢話講完即刻開始出發 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nDay 1<br />\n<br />\n又係坐快運, 而家呢班夜機已經無左<br />\n其實以前早去晚回時間真係好好 <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/9LiCpL0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9LiCpL0.jpg&h=00e0dc0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCheck In 時地勤問我坐緊急通道位好唔好, 梗係即刻話好啦<br />\n上機後有個空姐來Check登機證, 之後解釋注意事項<br />\n問題係呢個空姐應該係日/韓籍, D英文好難聽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後咩都聽唔明, 就咁OKOK就算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zhqEhWF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzhqEhWF.jpg&h=dc8dfba0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n落機後搭巴士去市區, 又多人又慢<br />\n就快搭到訓著 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/l3JDouj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fl3JDouj.jpg&h=e8898f27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到酒店丟低D行李即刻出一中街搵野食<br />\n已經九點幾<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/RCybL2S.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRCybL2S.jpg&h=bbb5ddbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實事隔太耐, 已經唔係好記得食過乜<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/KsB9SKh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKsB9SKh.jpg&h=180edb15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舟車勞頓其實無乜胃口, 食左少少野就番酒店<br />\n頂樓有個common room, 望出去都幾開揚<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/PmfBjAP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FPmfBjAP.jpg&h=eeb1286a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚住呢D類似Hostel形式的床位<br />\n因為星期六, 要650台幣一晚<br />\n張相係第二朝影<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/MdhWfna.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMdhWfna.jpg&h=80ef2b3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDay 1咁就完左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n聽日繼續打, 希望唔好爛尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你住巧合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f00cc2deb60f6a2a4b1d93b64b4df20ac2445a0","tid":100131,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:20:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n你住巧合<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n奇異果"},{"pid":"1a1a3be24150c5b4ce8e90d474bf63e62db0f11f","tid":100131,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T13:27:07.000Z","msg":"下一頁貼埋最後一日D相, 埋埋個尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}